61
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:39,430
I think he's a good guy.

62
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,680
He's handsome and nice.

63
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:41,670
That brother of yours

64
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,240
