00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:03,790
(What are you doing?)

567
00:34:03,830 --> 00:34:05,030
(Are you asleep?)

568
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:06,390
(Why are you)

569
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:07,440
